Plasma in the flux tube has a pressure P

59
00:03:33,688 --> 00:03:38,974
and the plasma outside the flux tube
has a pressure Pext.

60
00:03:39,136 --> 00:03:42,676
This flux tube has a magnetic field B

61
00:03:42,744 --> 00:03:45,513
which is much larger 
than the magnetic field [Bext]

62
