90
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:32,348
towards the surface of the Sun.

91
00:05:34,060 --> 00:05:38,580
Once flux ropes have emerged
from the interior through the surface,

92
00:05:38,983 --> 00:05:40,794
how will they interact?

93
00:05:40,794 --> 00:05:43,812
And how their magnetic fields will evolve?

94
00:05:44,659 --> 00:05:48,284
The image on the left shows
