95
00:05:48,284 --> 00:05:50,043
from the previous movie,

96
00:05:50,043 --> 00:05:52,733
the image on the right has been processed

97
00:05:52,733 --> 00:05:56,523
to highlight the edges of each flux loop

98
00:05:56,523 --> 00:05:58,871
and make the structure more clear.

99
00:05:59,774 --> 00:06:01,866
Now, for the sake of the discussion,

100
00:06:01,866 --> 00:06:05,077
let's suppose that the magnetic fields
