can be neglected.

188
00:11:40,425 --> 00:11:42,937
The plasma is incompressible

189
00:11:44,812 --> 00:11:47,961
and we assume 
a two-dimensional geometry

190
00:11:48,056 --> 00:11:51,478
with d/dy = 0.

191
00:11:54,747 --> 00:11:56,631
To derive the Sweet-Parker model,

192
00:11:56,631 --> 00:12:00,002
we will use the <i>Continuity Equation,</i>
the <i>Ohm's Law</i>

193
00:12:00,002 --> 00:12:01,664
and the <i>Equation of Motion.</i>

194
