divided by its length.

227
00:14:06,839 --> 00:14:10,854
The question is, how do we determine
the outflow velocity?

228
00:14:12,061 --> 00:14:14,829
We will use the <i>Equation of Motion.</i>

229
00:14:19,268 --> 00:14:22,282
Let's write down
the MHD equation of motion

230
00:14:22,282 --> 00:14:24,438
for a steady state plasma.

231
00:14:27,342 --> 00:14:29,258
Let's now consider the current sheet

232
